name: Divine Serpent Geh
text: Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must be Special Summoned with "Orichalcos Shunoros", and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. If this card is Summoned: Send your entire hand to the Graveyard, also you lose all your LP. Cannot declare an attack unless you send the top 10 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. You cannot lose the Duel.
